responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "EBE4E7BD4B4CA49D16E8A685F2B097C3", "No. NO! Dugal was living in Lionhold. He would not leave the walls without telling me. MY LITTLE BROTHER! This cannot be. How could they add his name to their list. He is my family! First I lose my older brother, then this. I am alone. Why? Leave me. Please, leave me.")
